a2t.text_actual: Make any photo into a funny one.   CNET :  ”If you are searching for a great time killer and funny photo app, this one is for you. This app promises many laughs as you twist and edit your friends' faces.”   Main Features:  Replace face parts  Funny eyes, noses, make them bald.  Smudge and warp  Make faces thin or fat, make ears pointy, make them smile.  Packed with features  Add text or draw on top of the photo, Share with friends. Simple to use, easy to learn and share.
